{"tid":2342722,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡依林緊身「抬腳一字馬」形狀被看光！微歪頭雪乳傾倒而出","createTime":"2020-12-27T10:49:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T12:35:00.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fc4a15b462c521caf6a52b533adb7bc48990165b","tid":2342722,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T10:49:54.000Z","msg":"40歲天后蔡依林少女般的凍齡美顏讓許多粉絲都驚訝她的真實年齡。她日前結束高雄6場「Ugly Beauty」巡迴演唱會後，馬不停蹄再曝光新MV《甜秘密》，不斷給粉絲新驚喜的她，近日又PO出一字馬的超軟Q辣照，讓粉絲讚嘆不已。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/09/28/2797905-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F09%2F28%2F2797905-PH.jpg&h=8086f939&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲蔡依林。（圖／翻攝自蔡依林IG）<br />\n<br />\n蔡依林在近日為了代言運動品牌，穿上貼身的藍色瑜珈服，展現小蠻腰跟全身沒有多餘的贅肉，她展現包括一字馬在內的各種專業伸展姿勢，身材曲線一覽無遺，充滿性感的自信美。廣告代言不斷的她也回顧了下今年接到的品牌代言，還不忘俏皮幫外送平台打廣告：「想說午餐吃什麼好。」相當敬業<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/27/2956504-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F27%2F2956504-PH.jpg&h=7b1dd661&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲蔡依林穿上貼身的藍色瑜珈服。（圖／翻攝自蔡依林IG）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/27/2956506-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F27%2F2956506-PH.jpg&h=23716fa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼蔡依林擺出一字馬等專業姿勢。（圖／翻攝自蔡依林IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/27/2956505-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F27%2F2956505-PH.jpg&h=ba9309a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上，蔡依林近日的新MV話題度可說是攻佔娛樂版面，找來鬼才導演廖人帥執導，一開頭由老高與小茉擔任說書人，講述漁村中的美人魚秘辛。蔡依林飾演的少女則因為小時候曾被被鯨豚救了一命，成為一個忠實的鯨豚迷。甚至挺著孕肚現身漁人酒吧，並誕下人魚寶寶，創新程度立刻登上熱搜。"},{"pid":"b8c512fc7107931205899e57542729f7b0b795ca","tid":2342722,"uid":58958,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T10:51:20.000Z","msg":"佢啲歌行得好前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af4c0629cc49e17ec95f05aaabc28966b60bdf5","tid":2342722,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T11:10:47.000Z","msg":"雪乳<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a19dd2d422774e088046e07a3875057daf5ad7","tid":2342722,"uid":132262,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T11:15:19.000Z","msg":"估唔到佢啲腳趾咁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日著尖頭鞋 腳趾應該會外彎架喎"},{"pid":"b602e0804b479011c5ecf662cffdcc66dcd792b2","tid":2342722,"uid":261937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T11:16:54.000Z","msg":"40碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"851e142291e40354b115935069b8b26f14dfdc6f","tid":2342722,"uid":156652,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T11:16:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hsn7YtC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHsn7YtC.jpg&h=af0e5689&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6c92ec7e9467ae737bf13d2df217134197f2cad","tid":2342722,"uid":90601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b8c512fc7107931205899e57542729f7b0b795ca","tid":2342722,"uid":58958,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T10:51:20.000Z","msg":"佢啲歌行得好前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T11:19:44.000Z","msg":"風水輪流轉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前係佢俾人笑 姐撚俾人吹奏<br />\n依家係姐撚俾人笑到落地底 jolin上左大台"},{"pid":"594a0bd96899466c81d920c